meanings.type: Godan verb with 'ru' ending, Intransitive verb
meanings.meaning: 1. to enter; to come in; to go in; to get in; to arrive Antonym: 出る目に砂が入りました。I got some sand in my eye.

meanings.type: Godan verb with 'ru' ending, Intransitive verb
meanings.meaning: 2. to join (a club, company, etc.); to enter (a university, the army, etc.); to enroll (in); to go into (e.g. politics); to get into 彼は大学へ進まず実業界に入った。He entered the business world instead of going on to college.

meanings.type: Godan verb with 'ru' ending, Intransitive verb
meanings.meaning: 3. to be contained (in); to be included (in); to be inside (e.g. a box); to come under (a heading); to belong (in a category) 箱の中にはりんごが６個入っている。There are six apples in the box.

meanings.type: Godan verb with 'ru' ending, Intransitive verb
meanings.meaning: 4. to (be able to) fit (in a container, building, etc.); to be (able to be) held; to be (able to be) accommodated この球場は５万人入る。This stadium will hold 50,000 people.

meanings.type: Godan verb with 'ru' ending, Intransitive verb
meanings.meaning: 5. to be introduced; to be brought in; to be installed

meanings.type: Godan verb with 'ru' ending, Intransitive verb
meanings.meaning: 6. to be received; to be obtained 彼は月収２０００ドルの金が入る。He has a monthly income of 2,000 dollars.

meanings.type: Godan verb with 'ru' ending, Intransitive verb
meanings.meaning: 7. to be scored (of points); to be won (of votes) わがチームは最終回で５点入った。Our team scored five runs in the last inning.

meanings.type: Godan verb with 'ru' ending, Intransitive verb
meanings.meaning: 8. to turn on; to start functioning; to start working

meanings.type: Godan verb with 'ru' ending, Intransitive verb
meanings.meaning: 9. to enter (a month, season, etc.); to reach (e.g. a climax); to get to (e.g. the main topic); to enter into (e.g. negotiations); to start (doing); to begin 梅雨に入った。The rainy season has set in.

meanings.type: Godan verb with 'ru' ending, Intransitive verb
meanings.meaning: 10. to form (of a crack, fissure, etc.); to develop

meanings.type: Godan verb with 'ru' ending, Intransitive verb
meanings.meaning: 11. to be put in (of effort, spirit, feeling, etc.); to be applied (e.g. of strength)

meanings.type: Godan verb with 'ru' ending, Intransitive verb
meanings.meaning: 12. to be ready (of tea, coffee, etc.); to be made

meanings.type: Godan verb with 'ru' ending, Intransitive verb
meanings.meaning: 13. to enter the body (of alcohol); to become drunk

9. to send (a fax); to call
